QuestData.Title: Bending Bars
QuestData.Description:
In all the chaos, the gates of the upper hold have been left open. If we slip through, they might not even notice us until it is too late.
One of Helya's lieutenants stands between us and Helgarde Keep. End them.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: This mawsworn subjugator leads the forces in Desmotaeron against the combined forces of the afterlives.
